{"word":"G1882 - ἐπανόρθωσις - epanórthōsis - ep-an-or'-tho-sis - Correction","slug":"G1882","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπανόρθωσις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epanórthōsis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-an-or'-tho-sis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Correction"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03B8;&#x03C9;&#x03C3;&#x03B9;&#x03C2; - epanortho&#x0304;sis</b> - <i>ep-an-or'-tho-sis</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G461\">G461</a>; a <i>straightening up again</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>rectification</i> (<i>reformation</i>): - correction."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1357\">G1357</a>, <a href=\"#/G3716\">G3716</a>, <a href=\"#/G3717\">G3717</a>, <a href=\"#/G3718\">G3718</a>, <a href=\"#/G3719\">G3719</a>, <a href=\"#/G3720\">G3720</a>, <a href=\"#/G3721\">G3721</a>, <a href=\"#/G3722\">G3722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3723\">G3723</a>"}]}